00:11:19.706 --> 00:11:20.340
literarily.
 

00:11:20.340 --> 00:11:24.073
Just as you know how to do a
literary reading of a novel,

00:11:24.073 --> 00:11:28.408
some modern scholars will do a
literary reading of the Gospels.

00:11:28.408 --> 00:11:30.288
It's a perfectly legitimate way
to read the Gospels;

00:11:30.288 --> 00:11:32.278
it's just not the one that I'm
going to concentrate on in this

00:11:32.278 --> 00:11:32.538
class.
 

00:11:32.538 --> 00:11:34.049
There are many others,
you could say,

00:11:34.049 --> 00:11:35.476
I'm going to do a
deconstructionist

00:11:35.476 --> 00:11:38.120
