00:22:04.049 --> 00:22:06.740
My John Wayne imitation for you.
 

00:22:06.740 --> 00:22:08.987
The centurion,
though, recognizes that Jesus

00:22:08.987 --> 00:22:11.442
is the Son of God,
at least according--if that's

00:22:11.442 --> 00:22:12.750
the way we read that.
 

00:22:12.750 --> 00:22:16.038
The other people who recognize
Jesus and understand are demons,

00:22:16.038 --> 00:22:17.630
at least they recognize him.
 

00:22:17.630 --> 00:22:20.430
Now let's look at the turning
point in the Gospel,

00:22:20.430 --> 00:22:21.808
