show you how I,

00:22:21.808 --> 00:22:26.818
as a brilliant modern scholar
,have posed these problems,

00:22:26.818 --> 00:22:29.818
the Messianic secret problem,
the problem of misunderstanding

00:22:29.818 --> 00:22:32.365
and all this sort of thing,
and the problem of the ending

00:22:32.365 --> 00:22:34.554
which I'll get to in a minute,
and I'm going to make it all

00:22:34.554 --> 00:22:35.328
makes sense for you.
 

00:22:35.328 --> 00:22:37.901
There are other scholars who
might not think I'm so brilliant

00:22:37.901 --> 00:22:39.315
and might have other
explanations,

00:22:39.315 --> 00:22:41.328
but this one's mine and I'm
sticking to it.

00:22:41.328 --> 00:22:46.384
8:27--follow along with me,
in your hymnals,

00:22:46.384 --> 00:22:53.554
8:27 "Jesus went on with
his disciples to the villages of

00:22:53.554 --> 00:22:56.140
Caesarea Philippi.
 

00:22:56.140 --> 00:22:57.740
And on the way he asked his
