00:23:36.440 --> 00:23:37.720
There it is again.
 

00:23:37.720 --> 00:23:40.390
Peter confesses correctly,
"You are the

00:23:40.390 --> 00:23:42.191
Messiah,"
and Jesus says,

00:23:42.191 --> 00:23:43.930
okay don't tell anybody.
 

00:23:43.930 --> 00:23:47.390
Jesus is not a very good
evangelist, apparently.

00:23:47.390 --> 00:23:51.509
He's not Joel Olsteen or
whoever that guy is in Houston.

00:23:51.509 --> 00:23:53.462
He's not the kind who's
proclaiming it all out,

00:23:53.462 --> 00:23:55.289
at least according to the
Gospel of Mark.

00:23:55.289 --> 00:23:57.838
Then he began to teach them.
 

00:23:57.838 --> 00:23:59.880
Now wait a minute that might be
important.

00:23:59.880 --> 00:24:03.282
He just did this command to
silence, what does the next

00:24:03.282 --> 00:24:04.038
verse say?
 

00:24:04.038 --> 00:24:06.806
"Then he began to teach
them that the Son of Man must

00:24:06.806 --> 00:24:08.358
